52:48.224 --> 52:51.627
Also, I have a buddy
I really need to call.

53:04.279 --> 53:06.281
-Five minutes.

53:14.488 --> 53:15.509
[ <i>Country music plays</i> ]

53:15.609 --> 53:17.871
[ Cellphone rings ]

53:17.972 --> 53:20.674
♪♪♪

