She's got a video.

54:09.659 --> 54:11.200
<i>-Hey, guys!</i>
<i>Natasha here.</i>

54:11.300 --> 54:13.482
<i>Today, I'm gonna show y'all</i>
<i>how to do a super-pretty,</i>

54:13.582 --> 54:16.285
