54:18.627 --> 54:20.609
-Is there contact details
on there?

54:20.709 --> 54:22.411
-What are we doing here?

54:22.511 --> 54:25.854
-Okay, your client David Oumou,
he's going to insist

54:25.954 --> 54:27.775
