on the movie.

54:27.876 --> 54:29.657
<i>-I only use Shade-Stix</i>
<i>by Bella Ross.</i>

54:29.757 --> 54:33.341
-Okay. I mean, you know,
makeup's makeup, I guess.

54:33.441 --> 54:35.943
[ Buzzer ]

54:36.043 --> 54:37.544
-Keep it moving.

54:37.645 --> 54:40.527
[ Indistinct shouting
in distance ]

