55:31.974 --> 55:33.976
[ Handcuff clicking ]

55:37.139 --> 55:39.141
-Yago!

55:39.661 --> 55:42.264
[ Shuttlecock thudding ]

55:44.266 --> 55:46.267
[ Thudding continues ]

55:47.949 --> 55:49.951
-Yeah!

55:51.272 --> 55:53.334
[ Laughing ] Oh!

55:53.434 --> 55:55.696
