56:20.419 --> 56:22.561
-[ Groans ]

56:22.661 --> 56:26.164
-It's me, motherfuckers!

56:26.264 --> 56:28.366
Come on, man!

56:28.466 --> 56:31.789
[ Wind gusting ]

