57:07.662 --> 57:09.123
-We'll get there, Shorty.

57:09.223 --> 57:10.605
You and me.

57:10.705 --> 57:12.406
-How?

57:12.506 --> 57:14.648
-Fuck if I know.

57:14.748 --> 57:17.071
But we will.

57:21.234 --> 57:23.496
[ Man shouting indistinctly ]

57:23.597 --> 57:25.699
-Come on!
